divs: Sighting DetailsWhile pulling up to a stop sign at Moss Mill & Vienna Ave I noticed in the sky in front of me what appeared to be a Large craft moving slowly but some of which was obscured by a cloud. It appeared to be two shades of dark gray and black I would say circular in shape but I guess it was the bottom that I saw and it was not flat it had indentations. I turned down Moss Mill to get a better look but it was gone. I looked all over and wondered if I really saw what I thought I saw. I also thought to myself why arent I scared.
